  "detailed_description": "Vyanka Silverlight is a monster huntress who was called to her home village to protect it from a great evil that ravages its lands. Her grandfather was attacked by a vampire and lost his memory. Take on the role of this intrepid huntress and defeat enemies trying to destroy your home while recovering your grandfather's memories.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- Game Mechanics -</h2></strong><br><br>Defeat monsters to regain your powers. Each monster contains a memory of Vyanka, so eradicate them all in each biome to evolve the character.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/2c6a6f53c62e104ba7dc9c86562a60af.poster.avif?t=1741748911\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/2c6a6f53c62e104ba7dc9c86562a60af.webm?t=1741748911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/2c6a6f53c62e104ba7dc9c86562a60af.mp4?t=1741748911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the most diverse biomes in search of powers spread across each map. Discover secrets and evolve the character to her full power.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More than 40 different monsters to dominate.</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/48d910a2f8829d08a7b9b594a41124f6.poster.avif?t=1741748911\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/48d910a2f8829d08a7b9b594a41124f6.webm?t=1741748911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/48d910a2f8829d08a7b9b594a41124f6.mp4?t=1741748911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Discover Familiars to aid in your exploration and combat.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slay bosses and gain their powers</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/7a7bf85f9ee9290a6cc24300e8712d59.poster.avif?t=1741748911\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/7a7bf85f9ee9290a6cc24300e8712d59.webm?t=1741748911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/7a7bf85f9ee9290a6cc24300e8712d59.mp4?t=1741748911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>15 exclusive biomes to explore.",
  "about_the_game": "Vyanka Silverlight is a monster huntress who was called to her home village to protect it from a great evil that ravages its lands. Her grandfather was attacked by a vampire and lost his memory. Take on the role of this intrepid huntress and defeat enemies trying to destroy your home while recovering your grandfather's memories.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- Game Mechanics -</h2></strong><br><br>Defeat monsters to regain your powers. Each monster contains a memory of Vyanka, so eradicate them all in each biome to evolve the character.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/2c6a6f53c62e104ba7dc9c86562a60af.poster.avif?t=1741748911\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/2c6a6f53c62e104ba7dc9c86562a60af.webm?t=1741748911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/2c6a6f53c62e104ba7dc9c86562a60af.mp4?t=1741748911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the most diverse biomes in search of powers spread across each map. Discover secrets and evolve the character to her full power.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More than 40 different monsters to dominate.</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/48d910a2f8829d08a7b9b594a41124f6.poster.avif?t=1741748911\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/48d910a2f8829d08a7b9b594a41124f6.webm?t=1741748911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/48d910a2f8829d08a7b9b594a41124f6.mp4?t=1741748911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Discover Familiars to aid in your exploration and combat.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slay bosses and gain their powers</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/7a7bf85f9ee9290a6cc24300e8712d59.poster.avif?t=1741748911\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/7a7bf85f9ee9290a6cc24300e8712d59.webm?t=1741748911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115150/extras/7a7bf85f9ee9290a6cc24300e8712d59.mp4?t=1741748911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>15 exclusive biomes to explore.",
